1. Start Minikube:
powershell
minikube start --driver=docker

2. Point PowerShell to Minikube Docker:
powershell
& minikube -p minikube docker-env --shell powershell | Invoke-Expression

3. Build Docker image:
powershell
docker build -t banking-case-manager:latest .

4. Deploy with Helm:
powershell
helm install banking-case-manager ./chart

5. Access your app:
powershell
minikube ip
# Open http://<minikube-ip>:30080/

6. Update app:
powershell
docker build -t banking-case-manager:latest .
helm upgrade banking-case-manager ./chart

7. Uninstall:
powershell
helm uninstall banking-case-manager

